{"tid":2312640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禁煙奇招｜三藩市住宅居民將被禁家裏吸煙 大麻除外","createTime":"2020-12-05T06:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T06:55:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df0ad316d78f19cf5f5a320aadb1a135b3af08b1","tid":2312640,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國三藩市參議會（San Francisco Board of Supervisors）周二以10票贊成，1票反對，一讀通過一項新法案，以保護居民免受室內二手煙的毒害。法案將禁止民眾在三個單位或以上的樓宇和所有公共場所內吸煙，但醫用大麻則獲豁免。若法案最終通過，住宅居民將被禁止在自己家裏吸煙，屢犯者每天罰款1,000美元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201205/MFB7JCAI6NBGVEQ5TGD52KUOSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201205%2FMFB7JCAI6NBGVEQ5TGD52KUOSA%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=86896894\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201205%2FMFB7JCAI6NBGVEQ5TGD52KUOSA%2F&h=205e5550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201205/MFB7JCAI6NBGVEQ5TGD52KUOSA/</a>"},{"pid":"7ffa4b9944d32003d3b5c4757e6147b7949d5456","tid":2312640,"uid":76705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"等上court比人推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d84b12651aaaa13b68723461851bbc3f197643","tid":2312640,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔俾自己屋企食煙 , 左膠思維"},{"pid":"dddc20a0ee1d8434c7d077541abc68335b19d3c8","tid":2312640,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"係時候全球禁煙了 食大麻好過"}]}